  <summary date="2017-07-27T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Care Corps Demonstration Act of 2017

This bill amends the Public Health Service Act to authorize the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to implement a local care corps program through which eligible volunteers perform care services for individuals with a disability or individuals who have difficulty with self-care or living independently.</summary>
